    Interesting design, but rings hollow when considering the main goals of a stay. Elite membership benefits not honored.
    I decided to give this location on the Llobregat side a try. The hotel itself is an interesting property at first, but you quickly realize that its a lot of style over substance. The rooms open up directly to the outdoor, like a fire escape or a US motel. Many other guests complained about feeling dizzy and acrophobic even on the short walk from their room to the glass elevator.
    Interiors are on the newer side, as the hotel is only about 10 years old. However, the shower is extremely slippery due to the easy-clean ultra-smooth surface lining the interior of the bathroom.
    I think the most disappointing part of the stay was that despite ample capacity my Bonvoy elite benefits as Platinum were not honored. I got a standard, I see youre a very loyal guest but nothing else afterwards, like we tried our best to give you a higher floor but we were booked full, or we didnt have any upgrades for you. Again, its not that I expected the request would be fulfilled, but it seemed like they werent even acknowledged.
    Finally, location is incredibly inconvenient if youre commuting to anywhere in city center or further out like Poblenou. This was a huge mistake and cost me valuable time going from meeting to meeting in Barcelona traffic.

    About this hotel

    In 2 towers on Plaa d'Europa square, this upscale hotel next to EuropaFira station is an 8-minute walk from the Fira de BarcelonaGran Via convention center.

    Contemporary rooms feature flat-screen TVs, iPod docks and Wi-Fi (fee), as well as minifridges and coffeemakers; some have balconies or terraces. Suites add sitting areas or separate living rooms. Upgraded suites feature whirlpool tubs; some add private hot tubs. Room service is available 24/7.

    There's a chic Mediterranean restaurant, an indoor pool, a hot tub and a gym. There's also a seasonal rooftop pool and bar.

    Check-in time: 3:00PM
    Check-out time: 12:00PM
